    "causal_summary": "Delete the length penalty logic from the cross-encoder reranker entirely. In an embedded RAG system the documents are fixed-size spec-doc artifacts -- penalizing 78.6% of the corpus for exceeding 2000 characters is counterproductive. Short-doc boosting (< 50 chars) is equally unjustified and should be removed in the same pass.",
